 nije baš išlo mojim tempom,

464
00:44:58,100 --> 00:44:59,560
 mojim putem kako sam ja gurao,

465
00:44:59,560 --> 00:45:02,020
 nego je gospodin nju malo drugim putem odvukao

466
00:45:02,020 --> 00:45:08,260
 i evo sad vidim da se i kod brata mog isto prekrasne stvari događaju.

467
00:45:08,260 --> 00:45:12,940
 Znači, vidim kako taj blagoslov koji je ušao u moju osnovnu obitelj,

468
00:45:12,940 --> 00:45:14,460
 znači da se preljeva na sve.

469
00:45:14,460 --> 00:45:20,640
 I evo, ja vjerujem da će to ići samo dalje i dalje.

470
00:45:21,100 --> 00:45:25,120
 Znači, odnosi kod nas su u istinu iscijeljeni,

471
00:45:25,120 --> 00:45:26,660
 znači da ja kad s braćom razgovaram,

472
00:45:26,660 --> 00:45:27,860
 mi razgovaramo iskreno,

473
00:45:27,860 --> 00:45:31,580
 nema više ovoga.

474
00:45:31,580 --> 00:45:32,960
 Ali dobro, da se sada vratim,

475
00:45:32,960 --> 00:45:36,340
 da se sad vratim možda na odnos sa suprugom.

476
00:45:36,340 --> 00:45:41,580
 Znači, nama je,

477
00:45:41,580 --> 00:45:45,300
 nakon tog iscijeljenja mog srca,

478
00:45:45,300 --> 00:45:47,280
 gdje sam ja doživio iskustvo Bože ljubavi,

479
00:45:47,280 --> 00:45:50,220
 ja sam jednostavno odlučio

480
00:45:50,220 --> 00:45:51,860
 da više,

481
00:45:51,860 --> 00:45:54,260
 da meni nije u mojom životu

482
00:45:54,260 --> 00:45:55,420
 najvažnija Katarina,

483
00:45:55,420 --> 00:45:57,160
 nego Isus.

484
00:45:57,160 --> 00:46:01,060
 I ja ću u stvari činiti radi Isusa,

485
00:46:01,060 --> 00:46:02,920
 ne radi Katarine,

486
00:46:02,920 --> 00:46:04,560
 ili radi bilo koga drugog.

487
00:46:04,560 --> 00:46:08,960
 Isus se traži da ja ljubim svoju ženu.

488
00:46:08,960 --> 00:46:11,200
 Polako sam učio šta to znači

489
00:46:11,200 --> 00:46:13,920
 i polako sam bio,

490
00:46:13,920 --> 00:46:16,140
 vidio da ja moram biti onaj prvi

491
00:46:16,140 --> 00:46:18,400
 oprat suđe,

492
00:46:18,400 --> 00:46:19,460
 znači ja sam znao prije,

493
00:46:19,460 --> 00:46:20,620
 ono vidim suđe na večer,

494
00:46:20,620 --> 00:46:22,780
 ovdje ja spavat.

495
00:46:22,780 --> 00:46:25,140
 Ne, ne, ne, nema više.

496
00:46:25,140 --> 00:46:26,900
 Znači, ustajem se prvi,

497
00:46:26,900 --> 00:46:29,160
 ja ću, ja ću,

498
00:46:29,160 --> 00:46:32,040
 od tih nekih banalnih stvari

499
00:46:32,040 --> 00:46:33,500
 do toga da pretrpim,

500
00:46:33,500 --> 00:46:36,260
 kada moja suprava ima neko tjeskovno stanje,

501
00:46:36,260 --> 00:46:37,360
 pa mi iznosi to na

502
00:46:37,360 --> 00:46:38,860
 osebujan način,

503
00:46:38,860 --> 00:46:41,920
 da pretrpim,

504
00:46:41,920 --> 00:46:43,480
 da ne vraćam istom mjerom,

505
00:46:43,480 --> 00:46:44,880
 da spustim glavu.

506
00:46:45,440 --> 00:46:49,300
 Ja sam od tih godina isplako suze, suze, suze, suze, suze,

507
00:46:49,300 --> 00:46:50,720
 hvala Bogu na daru suza,

508
00:46:50,720 --> 00:46:54,060
 jer me je uistinu preko toga liječio.

509
00:46:54,060 --> 00:46:56,740
 Pasiju sam gledao valjda 50 puta,

510
00:46:56,740 --> 00:47:00,820
 toliko sam promatrao kako Isus reagira,

511
00:47:00,820 --> 00:47:02,840
 znači na neke uvrede,

512
00:47:02,840 --> 00:47:03,760
 na poniženja

513
00:47:03,760 --> 00:47:05,540
 i onu scenu,

514
00:47:05,540 --> 00:47:07,600
 scenu kad Isusu pljuvačka curi,

515
00:47:07,600 --> 00:47:10,760
 znači ja sam to fizički znao osjetiti nekada

516
00:47:10,760 --> 00:47:13,640
 od mojih najbližih,

517
00:47:13,640 --> 00:47:15,720
 od supruge nekada,

518
00:47:15,720 --> 00:47:17,240
 ba i u drugim odnosima,

519
00:47:17,240 --> 00:47:18,180
 ali ja sam,

520
00:47:18,180 --> 00:47:20,340
 koji sam bio prije Minsko polje,

521
00:47:20,340 --> 00:47:22,780
 ja sam imao snagu prešutjet,

522
00:47:22,780 --> 00:47:23,740
 blagoslivljati,

523
00:47:23,740 --> 00:47:24,960
 i kako se,

524
00:47:24,960 --> 00:47:27,980
 tako kak se mijenjava taj odnos moj

525
00:47:27,980 --> 00:47:29,960
 prema drugima,

526
00:47:29,960 --> 00:47:31,620
 tako su se drugi počeli mijenjati

527
00:47:31,620 --> 00:47:35,040
 premeni i gospodin je,

528
00:47:35,040 --> 00:47:38,320
 gospodin je to uistinu

529
00:47:38,320 --> 00:47:42,220
 isciljivao u braku,

530
00:47:42,220 --> 00:47:43,340
 tada smo imali,

531
00:47:43,340 --> 00:47:45,260
 imali smo dvoje djece,

532
00:47:45,260 --> 00:47:47,440
 tako do obraćenja mojeg,

533
00:47:47,440 --> 00:47:48,620
 znači i marina našeg,

534
00:47:48,620 --> 00:47:50,120
 smo dobili dvijedaneste,

535
00:47:50,120 --> 00:47:52,140
 onda nas je gospodin blagoslovio još

536
00:47:52,140 --> 00:47:55,760
 sa troje dječice

537
00:47:55,760 --> 00:47:57,740
 i imamo još tri bebe u nebu,

538
00:47:57,740 --> 00:48:00,980
 hvala i slavo Isusu na to,

539
00:48:01,060 --> 00:48:03,200
 evo jedna od tih beba je prije dva mjeseca

540
00:48:03,200 --> 00:48:05,480
 otešla u nebo

541
00:48:05,480 --> 00:48:08,980
 i sjećam se,

542
00:48:08,980 --> 00:48:10,760
 odnosno bili smo,

543
00:48:10,760 --> 00:48:11,840
 Katarina i ja,

544
00:48:11,840 --> 00:48:14,080
 smo se radovali bebi,

545
00:48:14,080 --> 00:48:22,080
 kad smo izgubili bebu u tim trenuticima,

546
00:48:22,080 --> 00:48:23,940
 ja nisam očajavao,

547
00:48:23,940 --> 00:48:25,380
 nego sam tužan,

548
00:48:25,380 --> 00:48:26,340
 sam bio plakao sam,

549
00:48:26,340 --> 00:48:27,340
 ali iz mene je izlazilo,

550
00:48:27,340 --> 00:48:28,140
 hvala Isuse.

551
00:48:29,940 --> 00:48:32,200
 od jednog čovjeka koji je

552
00:48:32,200 --> 00:48:34,620
 proklinjao,

553
00:48:34,620 --> 00:48:35,380
 koji je tražio,

554
00:48:35,380 --> 00:48:38,440
 koji je došlo do toga

555
00:48:38,440 --> 00:48:40,840
 da je iz mog srca izlazi

556
00:48:40,840 --> 00:48:41,920
 za hvalnost,

557
00:48:41,920 --> 00:48:42,700
 evo ja ne znam,

558
00:48:42,700 --> 00:48:43,980
 možda sam se sad izgubio stane,

559
00:48:43,980 --> 00:48:44,920
 molim te pomozi mi,

560
00:48:44,920 --> 00:48:45,840
 pomozi mi negdje,

561
00:48:45,840 --> 00:48:48,360
 možda sam otišao

562
00:48:48,360 --> 00:48:49,880
 pre daleko,

563
00:48:51,000 --> 00:48:52,840
 puno mi je to lakše islo na kavi,

564
00:48:52,840 --> 00:48:54,320
 moram ti reći.

565
00:48:54,320 --> 00:48:59,060
 Evo, ne znam,

566
00:48:59,060 --> 00:48:59,740
 možda sad,

567
00:48:59,740 --> 00:49:01,720
 ne znam što reći,

568
00:49:01,720 --> 00:49:03,240
 možda ako neko ima neka pitanja,

569
00:49:03,240 --> 00:49:05,060
 možda mi je lakše tako pričati,

570
00:49:05,060 --> 00:49:05,860
 konkretno ovako,

571
00:49:05,860 --> 00:49:06,400
 jedan na jedan,

572
00:49:06,400 --> 00:49:07,200
 nego ovako,

573
00:49:07,200 --> 00:49:09,060
 mikrofon.

574
00:49:09,060 --> 00:49:09,720
 Hvala vam.

